.ie \n(.g .ds Aq \(aq
.el .ds Aq '
.TH syncweb 1  "syncweb " 
.SH NAME
syncweb \- Delay\-tolerant web surfing
.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBsyncweb\fR [\fB\-\-verbose\fR] [\fB\-\-json\fR] [\fB\-\-no\-color\fR] [\fB\-\-data\-dir\fR] [\fB\-h\fR|\fB\-\-help\fR] <\fIsubcommands\fR>
.SH DESCRIPTION
Delay\-tolerant web surfing
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-\-verbose\fR
Enable verbose structured logging
.TP
\fB\-\-json\fR
Emit machine\-readable JSON where supported
.TP
\fB\-\-no\-color\fR
Disable colored output
.TP
\fB\-\-data\-dir\fR \fI<DATA_DIR>\fR [default: .syncweb]
Directory used for persistent node identity and data
.TP
\fB\-h\fR, \fB\-\-help\fR
Print help
.SH SUBCOMMANDS
.TP
syncweb\-version(1)
Show syncweb version information
.TP
syncweb\-repl(1)
Start an interactive command shell
.TP
syncweb\-start(1)
Start the local syncweb node for one command invocation
.TP
syncweb\-shutdown(1)
Stop the local syncweb node
.TP
syncweb\-create(1)
Create a synchronized folder
.TP
syncweb\-join(1)
Join a folder from an Iroh document ticket
.TP
syncweb\-leave(1)
Leave and remove a synchronized folder
.TP
syncweb\-unsubscribe(1)
Unsubscribe from a folder\*(Aqs live sync loop
.TP
syncweb\-folders(1)
List managed folders
.TP
syncweb\-devices(1)
Show this device\*(Aqs Iroh and Syncthing identities
.TP
syncweb\-config(1)
Show or update local configuration
.TP
syncweb\-ls(1)
List files in a local folder
.TP
syncweb\-find(1)
Search local files
.TP
syncweb\-sort(1)
Sort local files by discovery criteria
.TP
syncweb\-stat(1)
Show detailed metadata for a local file
.TP
syncweb\-download(1)
Download folder content or copy a local file
.TP
syncweb\-import(1)
Import local files into a synchronized folder
.TP
syncweb\-snapshot(1)
Manage content\-addressed snapshots
.TP
syncweb\-health(1)
Show seeding status per folder blob
.TP
syncweb\-init(1)
Initialize a folder and print a shareable URL
.TP
syncweb\-automatic(1)
Run rules\-based automatic synchronization
.TP
syncweb\-watch(1)
Watch a folder and import filesystem changes
.TP
syncweb\-stats(1)
Show persisted bandwidth accounting
.TP
syncweb\-verify(1)
Re\-check local folder blob integrity
.TP
syncweb\-schedule(1)
Show or update synchronization schedules
.TP
syncweb\-subscribe(1)
Subscribe to a folder with event filters
.TP
syncweb\-publish(1)
Publish a folder or blob for public read access
.TP
syncweb\-unpublish(1)
Remove a public blob pin
.TP
syncweb\-collection(1)
Create and publish versioned content collections
.TP
syncweb\-package(1)
Manage locally installed collection packages
.TP
syncweb\-network(1)
Network connectivity utilities
.TP
syncweb\-indexing(1)
Manage opt\-in indexing, catalogs, and metadata
.TP
syncweb\-link(1)
Create and resolve stable syncweb links
.TP
syncweb\-mirror(1)
Register alternate content providers
.TP
syncweb\-trust(1)
Inspect and delegate local trust
.TP
syncweb\-attest(1)
Sign content provenance attestations
.TP
syncweb\-report(1)
Submit a local moderation report
.TP
syncweb\-moderation(1)
Manage local moderation decisions
.TP
syncweb\-completions(1)
Generate shell completions
.TP
syncweb\-manpages(1)
Generate manpages
.TP
syncweb\-help(1)
Print this message or the help of the given subcommand(s)
